    MMRPRO

    MMRPRO.Rd

    Runs PanelPRO with genes = c("MLH1", "MSH2", "MSH6") and cancers = c("Colorectal", "Endometrial"), as in PanelPRO:::MODELPARAMS$MMRPRO.

    MMRPRO(...)

    Arguments

    ...

    Additional arguments to be passed into PanelPRO.

    See also

    PanelPRO

    Other predefined: BRCAPRO5(), BRCAPRO6(), BRCAPRO(), PanelPRO11(), PanelPRO22()

    Examples

    data(test_fam_3)
MMRPRO(test_fam_3, parallel = FALSE)
#> Your model has 2 cancers - Colorectal, Endometrial and 3 genes - MLH1_hetero_anyPV, MSH2_hetero_anyPV, MSH6_hetero_anyPV.
